00:23:55,797 --> 00:23:57,841
Edisi khusus!

207
00:23:57,925 --> 00:23:59,760
Takeo Arishima bunuh diri
bersama kekasihnya!

208
00:23:59,843 --> 00:24:00,969
Edisi khusus!

209
00:24:02,679 --> 00:24:04,431
Edisi khusus!

210
00:24:09,853 --> 00:24:12,731
Jika cinta terlarang
menyebabkan penderitaan,

211
00:24:14,066 --> 00:24:15,984
kau akhiri saja.

212
00:24:16,276 --> 00:24:17,945
Kenapa sampai bertindak drastis?

213
00:24:20,030 --> 00:24:23,617
Kesepian yang terasa
setelah mereka berpisah

214
00:24:24,660 --> 00:24:26,036
pasti membuat mereka takut.

215
00:24:28,121 --> 00:24:30,457
Pada akhirnya, kita akan lupa.

216
00:24:40,050 --> 00:24:41,927
Bagaimanapun, semoga sukses, U-jin.

217
00:25:00,487 --> 00:25:03,407
Kau juga, Sim-deok.

218
00:25:58,714 --> 00:26:01,925
LIMA TAHUN KEMUDIAN

219
00:26:02,009 --> 00:26:03,237
PERUSAHAAN REKANAN TAK TERBATAS SANGSEONG

220
00:26:03,270 --> 00:26:05,147
DONGJIN ILBO

221
00:26:07,524 --> 00:26:08,358
Masuk.

222
00:26:14,130 --> 00:26:15,006
Ini korannya.

223
00:26:16,007 --> 00:26:17,425
- Terima kasih.
- Sama-sama.

224
00:26:41,824 --> 00:26:44,369
PENYANYI YUN SIM-DEOK TAMPIL DI DANSUNGSA

225
00:26:48,248 --> 00:26:49,290
Jika ada kesempatan

226
00:26:50,258 --> 00:26:52,343
untuk tampil di sini kelak,

227
00:26:54,512 --> 00:26:57,265
maukah kau datang menontonku?

228
00:27:15,241 --> 00:27:16,409
Sim-deok.

229
00:27:22,582 --> 00:27:24,000
U-jin?

230
00:27:28,254 --> 00:27:30,006
Mustahil itu dia.

231
00:29:03,933 --> 00:29:09,105
UNTUK U-JIN

232
00:29:13,151 --> 00:29:18,114
