233
00:29:22,952 --> 00:29:25,747
"WAVES OF THE DANUBE"

234
00:30:45,159 --> 00:30:46,327
U-jin!

235
00:30:52,875 --> 00:30:54,335
Itu kau, bukan?

236
00:31:25,408 --> 00:31:26,284
Sim-deok.

237
00:31:38,808 --> 00:31:41,058
EPISODE 4

238
00:31:50,125 --> 00:31:53,462
Apa kabar?

239
00:32:01,929 --> 00:32:03,472
Bisa luangkan waktu untukku?

240
00:32:05,224 --> 00:32:08,018
Tak akan lama. Hanya beberapa menit.

241
00:32:08,185 --> 00:32:09,812
Ayo ke suatu tempat dan bicara.

242
00:32:14,108 --> 00:32:15,067
Ganti pakaian dahulu.

243
